<p><a name="Pouring" id="Pouring"></a></p>
<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Tea&amp;action=edit&amp;section=49" title="Edit section: Pouring">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">Pouring</span></h2>
<p>You might find that pouring the water from some height helps to stir the tea bags around your cup.</p>
<p><a name="See_also" id="See_also"></a></p>
